        "🔤 <b>Transliteração:</b> Vehayah ki-yecheta ve'ashem veheshiv et-hagezelah asher gazal o et-ha'oshek asher ashak o et-hapikadon asher hafked ito o et-ha'avedah asher matza.<br>",
